metadata.name: The Road So Far
metadata.description:
This picture perfectly describes the thorny path of Ukrainians to freedom. No matter how difficult it is, no matter how long, or whatever tangled paths our brothers take, we will still be free, united and independent.

Tanya Reckless, artist
Kyiv, Ukraine
Acrylic work: 35x45 cm
NFT: 1417x1906 px
